Lieutenant Schepbur is a gnome found at the Khazard Battlefield. He commands the battle tortoises, and even wears a tortoise shell as armour. He also mentions that more tortoises will be sent from the Tree Gnome Stronghold, as they are being trained there. He wears a tortoise shell at his back, and has a golden mace-like weapon that is shaped like a flattened tortoise.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • If he is given gnome food as a delivery in Gnome Restaurant, he'll say: "Soon, gnome cuisine will take over the world."
  • According to him, the tortoises he is currently using were trained in the Tree Gnome Stronghold, and the ones currently being trained there will be sent to him shortly.
